Near heath with 3m.

Young tree, lots of moss. Quite near some other saplings. Side note: Actual Corer depth 52 cm, and the probe 90 cm. And 52 established as maximum
Few saplings around, some difficulty with probe in determining depth at this point as well as some off measurements with soil moisture which showed very low readings on clearly wet soil
Lots of grass and moss. Very mossy under tree probe shows shallow

We see next to a small creek, marsh next to us south.
